Usage: set_cell_binding [-help] [-abstract ] [-lib <list_of_libs>] { -cell <list_of_cell_patterns> -view <list_of_views> }

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-abstract                              # abstract (bool, optional)
-cell <list_of_cell_patterns>          # Specifies one or more cell name
                                       # patterns to replace (string, required)
-lib <list_of_libs>                    # Specifies the OpenAccess library to
                                       # use to look for the cell abstracts
                                       # (string, required)
-view <list_of_views>                  # Specifies the cell view
                                       # (string, required)